рџЊ± Smart Farmer API
The backend REST API powering the Smart Farmer Assistant. It provides secure endpoints for user authentication and AI-driven agricultural support.

рџљЂ Features
JWT Authentication: Secure login and registration for Farmers, Buyers, and Providers.
AI Chat Engine: Integration with OpenAI to generate context-aware farming advice in Kinyarwanda.
Image Analysis: Vision API support for detecting crop diseases from uploaded photos.
Database: MongoDB with Mongoose for data persistence.
рџ›  Tech Stack
Runtime: Node.js
Framework: Express.js
Language: TypeScript
Database: MongoDB
AI: OpenAI API (gpt-4o-mini)
рџ”§ Installation
Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/Jackson-tj74/smart-farmer-api.git 
Install dependencies
npm install
Configure Environment VariablesCreate a .env file in the root directory:
PORT=5000NODE_ENV=development# DatabaseMONGODB_URI=mongodb://localhost:27017/smart-farmer# AuthJWT_SECRET=your-super-secret-jwt-key# OpenAIOPENAI_API_KEY=sk-your-openai-api-key-hereOPENAI_MODEL=gpt-4o-mini# Client URL (for CORS)CLIENT_URL=http://localhost:5173
Run the server
# Development mode with auto-reloadnpm run dev# Production modenpm run buildnpm start
The API will be available at http://localhost:5000.

